32
00:13:44,172 --> 00:14:04,912
which was a menthol, we can't help you. And I'll never forget that. So that was 35 years ago. So, I mean, and being a nursing now over at Mass Eye and Ear seeing all these patients young with asthma and having lots of troubles from the vaping. So really great work. Thank you.

33
